Title: Danfoss 077B B0 service thermostat (No.8)
Description: Designed to control the temperature in a refrigerator, upright or chest freezer, the Danfoss 077B B0 service thermostat is also compatible with bottle coolers and small commercial refrigeration appliances. Suitable for use as evaporator or room thermostats, the models in this range are available with normal function, fixed cut-in and cut-out temperature or constant or variable cut-in temperature for automatic defrost. A push button for semi-automatic defrost is also available. Normally closed (NC), this thermostat will cut out the compressor current circuit in response to a decrease in temperature.
